# ⚙️ 6. ITEM STRUCTURE (BEGINNER VERSION)

Every item has 4 simple parts:

* ID (system name) → ruby_key
* Name (player name) → “Gold Key”
* Icon → image file
* Purpose → what it does

---

# 🧠 7. ICON SOURCES (WHERE IMAGES COME FROM)

## 🟢 OPTION A — YOU UPLOAD THEM (BEST)

You create or download PNG files and place them in:

```
assets/icons/
```

---

## 🟡 OPTION B — FREE ONLINE ICONS (FOR TESTING)

Use temporary images while building:

* placeholder icons
* free icon libraries
* simple PNG downloads

---

## 🔴 OPTION C — AI GENERATED ICONS (OPTIONAL)

You can generate assets using prompts like:

